Approximately 15 acres, approximately 10 acres planted with UCB1 rootstock Randy/ Golden Hills variety 1440 trees Grafted in field 2018, nuts on trees 2021, the ground was deep ripped 2017 MID and Ag Well double drip system and soil monitor system 2017 New Ag Well permit #WP0015658 15HP Submersible Turbine 240V, 3 Phase Submersible turbine pump 240 deep, pump to deliver 130 GPM @ 160'PWL + 40 PSI at wellhead Also Drip system with filter station and booster pump, a new controller for filter station 2 -36"sand media filter, 3" butterfly valve gear op, steel pipe, flanges, gauge, air vents, manifolds, pressure relief value @ 65 PSI New Solar System to supply electricity for trees and home: elevated ground mount to easily store equipment under : 27 Axitec 385 watt commercial-grade solar panels, inverter located on array: paid off no contract Additional 3.5 acres pasture has MID flood irrigation House and barn sit on 1.5 acres, Miles creek runs through the property Mature Fruit trees on the property including : Fig, orange,2 cherry, peach, apricot, apple, and plum in the front yard Fenced Backyard: - 3360 sq ft Barn - stables for horses, New led lights throughout barn 560 sq ft Chicken coop Ranch Style Home 1504 sq ft - 7 rooms, 4 bedrooms, 2 baths Open Concept: Entryway, living, dining, and kitchen new porcelain plank-style flooring throughout a pocket door separates living quarters from sleeping quarters Great Natural light coming from french doors in the Living room leading to future deck or access to backyard Kitchen: New cabinets installed 2021 platinum grey shaker style with many upgrades like 2 trash can pull outs, spice and knife cabinets, All new stainless steel appliances 2021 french door refrigerator with pull drawer freezer, Double oven, oversized microwave, Peninsula has oversized stainless steel farm apron style sink, new dishwasher, and trash cabinet pull out for easy cleanup, waiting for new owner to pick counter tops and backsplash New Additional full Bathroom added to hallway 2017 the main bathroom updated 2017 new vanity and toilets 2020 New Eemax electric tankless water heater to replace bulky water heater and get rid of water closet Master bedroom with access to front yard, his and her closets with sitting area and fireplace
